Template: ejabberd-mod-mam/deprecation
Type: note
Description: ejabberd-mod-mam is deprecated in favor of ejabberd-mod-mam-mnesia.
 The new package is autoatmically installed, but please make sure you replace 
 "mod_mam" with "mod_mam_mnesia" in your config. mod_mam is now the name of the
 official package shipping with ejabberd since 15.06.
